{"tid":1736962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以聯署譴責加拿大領事館？佢完全漠視緊急求助（SOS)請求","createTime":"2019-11-18T23:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:18:44.000Z","uid":223407,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"57fe96eb05a25b7205505bb9d751d6203291b3d4","tid":1736962,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:35:51.000Z","msg":"無論你打咗幾多次電話，定係send咗幾多封email去佢哋個SOS郵箱，你都只會收到個難聽過粗口嘅回應：叫你遵從當地政府指引、叫你唔好去啲示威區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我啲email已經講咗好撚多次：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">polyU 入邊有你哋加拿大嘅留學生你哋加拿大係咪見死不救！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知點算，只係乜嘢都想試一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我見到網上有好多人喺加拿大領事館個網頁不停寫求救。我哋可唔可能將所有嘅名聯署，一次過擺上去，譴責加拿大政府見死不救？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟冇乜諗頭，不過如果大家如果覺得啱嘅話，比少少反應我，我哋就開始行動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝各位巴絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附上當局一篇仆街回應：<br />\n<br />\nGood day,<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nThank you for contacting the Emergency Watch and Response Centre at Global Affairs Canada in Ottawa.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nThe Government of Canada is closely monitoring developments in Hong Kong and takes the safety and security of Canadians abroad very seriously.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nCredible and timely travel information for Hong Kong is available on our  Travel Advice and Advisories webpage to enable you to make well-informed decisions regarding your stay and travel abroad. The decision to travel however, is solely the responsibility of the individual. The traveler is responsible for his or her own personal safety abroad.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nPlease be informed that the Canadian government does not provide personal physical security services. If your physical security is at risk, we recommend that you contact the local authorities, return to Canada or take other appropriate decisions to ensure your personal safety.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nIf you&rsquo;re currently in Hong Kong, we encourage you to take the following precautions:<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nMonitor local media for information and advice on upcoming demonstrations<br />\nFollow the instructions of local authorities<br />\nAvoid areas where demonstrations and large gatherings are taking place<br />\nMove away quickly and take shelter in a safe place if there are signs of civil disorder<br />\nCheck your flight status and the latest information provided by your airline before making your way to the airport<br />\nPlan to get to the airport well in advance of your flight&rsquo;s planned departure and go through Security and Immigration immediately upon arrival<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nGlobal Affairs Canada offers a registration service for all Canadians travelling or living abroad. This service is provided so that we can contact and assist you in the event of an emergency. Canadian citizens can register for free at <a href=\"http://travel.gc.ca/travelling/registration.\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.gc.ca%2Ftravelling%2Fregistration.&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=b4d2cf5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://travel.gc.ca/travelling/registration.</a> Canadians traveling abroad are encouraged to register on a voluntary basis.   It is by no means mandatory for Canadians travelling abroad to register."},{"pid":"5cdfd53d76828b25928c8a57fda4f0256df6886d","tid":1736962,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:36:10.000Z","msg":"For further information on the Registration of Canadians Abroad service, please consult <a href=\"http://travel.gc.ca/assistance/emergency-info/roca-faq.\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.gc.ca%2Fassistance%2Femergency-info%2Froca-faq.&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=90447a26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://travel.gc.ca/assistance/emergency-info/roca-faq.</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nWe encourage you to stay connected with the latest travel advice and advisories, via the web at <a href=\"http://travel.gc.ca\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.gc.ca&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=daae00a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://travel.gc.ca</a> our mobile TravelSmart application, available at <a href=\"http://travel.gc.ca/mobile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.gc.ca%2Fmobile&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=d107f24f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://travel.gc.ca/mobile</a> and our RSS feeds at <a href=\"http://travel.gc.ca/rss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.gc.ca%2Frss&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=54c355e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://travel.gc.ca/rss</a> You may also follow us on Twitter at <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/travelGoC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2FtravelGoC&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=d5117263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.twitter.com/travelGoC</a> or find us on Facebook at <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/travelGoC.\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FtravelGoC.&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=2fbdd68b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/travelGoC.</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nShould you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact the Emergency Watch and Response Centre (available 24/7) by responding to this email or dialing 613-996-8885 (call collect where available). During regular business hours, you can also speak directly with consular officials at the Consulate General of Canada in Hong Kong. For your convenience, please find their contact info below:<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nHong Kong - Consulate General of Canada<br />\n<br />\nStreet Address   9th Floor, 25 Westlands Road, Quarry Bay, Hong Kong SAR, China<br />\n<br />\nPostal Address   8th Floor, 25 Westlands Road, Quarry Bay, Hong Kong SAR, China<br />\n<br />\nTelephone   85 (2) 3719 4700<br />\n<br />\nFax   85 (2) 2847 7561<br />\n<br />\nEmail   hkong-cs@international.gc.ca<br />\n<br />\nInternet   www.hongkong.gc.ca"},{"pid":"31593d032cead7f27f2dd4c15631633e57b68662","tid":1736962,"uid":324266,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:36:46.000Z","msg":"我都係加拿大人但得的結果同你一樣"},{"pid":"47716243d629da96c9ac52ac81d48fd0e8362221","tid":1736962,"uid":223407,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"31593d032cead7f27f2dd4c15631633e57b68662","tid":1736962,"uid":324266,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:36:46.000Z","msg":"我都係加拿大人但得的結果同你一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:37:02.000Z","msg":"我哋聯署制唔制得過？"},{"pid":"ffa1441fcd5d645b984fcd335ccd031aa0f7d3a9","tid":1736962,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:37:54.000Z","msg":"[幫手置頂] 想贏嘅全部同我入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1736941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1736941</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"56ef4711bafe8818eab8c733dde554003ada100b","tid":1736962,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:40:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d632105c845da8fed0145f84b92213f17a9a126","tid":1736962,"uid":256837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:41:54.000Z","msg":"因為加拿大太子爺杜仔就係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /